WEBVTT

00:00:26.679 --> 00:00:31.056
For the first time, we could associate
the concept of cars

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:32.841
with the experience of silence.

00:00:33.824 --> 00:00:35.849
Cars can finally be quiet:

00:00:36.770 --> 00:00:38.223
peace in the streets,

00:00:38.247 --> 00:00:40.659
a silent revolution in the cities.

00:00:44.762 --> 00:00:51.143
(Hum)

00:00:53.659 --> 00:00:55.826
But silence can also be a problem.

00:00:56.801 --> 00:01:00.779
The absence of sound, in fact,
when it comes to cars,